<br>
Ear- Forest Loop<br>
Ear- Forest Loop<br>
Neck- Black Iron Medallion<br>
Face- Platinum Ruby Veil<br>
Head- Savant's Cap<br>
Finger- +7 wisdom ring <br>
Finger- +7 wisdom ring<br>
Wrist- Polished Bone Bracer<br>
Wrist- Runed Mithril Bracer<br>
Arm- Platinum Armband<br>
Hand- Splitpaw<br>
Shoulder- Braided Ivy Cord<br>
Chest- Crystal Covered Shroud<br>
Back- Rygorr Cloak<br>
Waist- Purity Belt<br>
Leg- Gator Leggings<br>
Feet- Wolf Hide Boot<br>
Primary- Velium Stone Etched Mace<br>
Secondary- Testament of Van.<br>
Range- Small Wisdom Diety<br>
<br>
Please keep in mind that this is my first character and started non-twinked.  Therefore, I don't have some high 60 seasoned player backing up my financials 8(  I'm trying to get to 200 wisdom by spending under 10k if possible (not including selling the ones I currently own, just pure spending)<br>
<br>
Much is appreciated.  Thank you.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umissfoxfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miss Foxfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/26/01 4:57:34 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://gwynhyfar.homestead.com/files/face.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> well... for level 37...</span><hr size=1> Ear- Forest Loop<br>
Ear- Forest Loop<br>
Neck- Black Iron Medallion > Chrysoberyl Talisman or better (new Tunare quests wield neck items for example)<br>
Face- > Velium Ruby Veil<br>
Head- Savant's Cap > Runed Circlet, Nightshade Wreath, or better<br>
Finger- +7 wisdom ring  <br>
Finger- +7 wisdom ring<br>
Wrist- Polished Bone Bracer > not that it matters, but maybe another RMB <br>
Wrist- Runed Mithril Bracer<br>
Arm- Platinum Armband > well, Ulthork Hide has 8 AC; these have none<br>
Hand- Splitpaw > Gnome Skin Gloves or better<br>
Shoulder- Braided Ivy Cord <br>
Chest- Crystal Covered Shroud<br>
Back- Rygorr Cloak > other choices: Molten and Mammoth Hide *sigh*<br>
Waist- Purity Belt > Try to group for a crystalline belt (Crystal Caverns)<br>
Leg- Gator Leggings<br>
Feet- Wolf Hide Boot > Imbued Mithril Studded Boots or Burynai Hide... or higher<br>
Primary- Velium Stone Etched Mace > Paw of Oppola... start your quest... <br>
Secondary- Testament of Van. > Charred Guardian Shield (+9 here, 10 AC)<br>
Range- Small Wisdom Diety <br>
<br>
Notice I did not mention GEBs or other stuff that you shouldn't bother with until later. If you're not twinked, my advice is to not get caught up in upper-level equipment. I didn't have a better shoulder item until 50. =\<br>
<br>
