</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uleandrasilvertongue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Leandra Silvertongue</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0> at: 4/27/01 7:25:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulyberniabelisama.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lybernia Belisama</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.sherilyn.net/pendulum/icon.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/27/01 8:50:43 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/sherilyn70/lybernia4a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Need help as a 37 Druid on wisdom desperately</span><hr size=1> Thanks Leandra  :)  Unfortunately I think most of the higher end items are still a little ways out of my reach since I'm still in Pendulum.  But at least I have some more ideas of what to look for in the future.  <br>
